{"title":"Melon/zh-CN","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Melon/zh-CN","type":"markdown","data":"**NetHack 中文 Wiki 需要您的帮助！**  \n[了解如何帮助我们完善Wiki](/wiki/NetHackWiki:How_to_help/zh-CN \"NetHackWiki:How to help/zh-CN\")\n\n**[English](/wiki/Melon \"Melon\")** • [中文（中国大陆）‎]()\n\n| % [![Melon.png](/images/1/19/Melon.png)](/wiki/File:Melon.png) |                                                                                                         |\n| -------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| 名称                                                             | 甜瓜                                                                                                      |\n| 基础价                                                            | 10 [zm](/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81 \"金币\")                                                                  |\n| 营养值                                                            | [100](/index.php?title=%E8%90%A5%E5%85%BB%E5%80%BC\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"营养值 (page does not exist)\") |\n| 食用所需回合数                                                        | 1                                                                                                       |\n| 重量                                                             | [5](/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"重量 (page does not exist)\")             |\n| 行为                                                             | [绝对素食](/index.php?title=%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"行为 (page does not exist)\")          |\n\n**甜瓜**（melon）是[NetHack](/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\")中的一种[可食用品](/wiki/%E5%8F%AF%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81 \"可食用品\")。它是[素食](/index.php?title=%E7%B4%A0%E9%A3%9F\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"素食 (page does not exist)\")类食物，适合于[绝对素食](/index.php?title=%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E7%B4%A0%E9%A3%9F\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"绝对素食 (page does not exist)\")行为。\n\n[ ]\n\n## Contents\n\n- [1 生成](#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90)\n\n- [2 描述](#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0)\n\n- [3 策略](#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5)\n\n- [4 历史](#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2)\n\n- [5 Variants](#Variants)\n\n  - [5.1 UnNetHack](#UnNetHack)\n  - [5.2 SpliceHack](#SpliceHack)\n\n- [6 百科文本](#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC)\n\n- [7 引用及注释](#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A)\n\n## 生成\n\n甜瓜在随机生成食物中占比1⁄100（1%）。\n\n[游客](/index.php?title=%E6%B8%B8%E5%AE%A2\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"游客 (page does not exist)\")在游戏开始时获得的随机食物里有可能出现甜瓜[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1)。\n\n[使用](/index.php?title=%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"使用 (page does not exist)\")有[充能](/index.php?title=%E5%85%85%E8%83%BD\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"充能 (page does not exist)\")的[丰饶之角](/index.php?title=%E4%B8%B0%E9%A5%B6%E4%B9%8B%E8%A7%92\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"丰饶之角 (page does not exist)\")有9⁄1000（0.9%）的概率产出1～2个甜瓜[\\[2\\]](#cite_note-2)。\n\n## 描述\n\n[食用](/wiki/%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%A8 \"食用\")甜瓜会获得100[营养值](/index.php?title=%E8%90%A5%E5%85%BB%E5%80%BC\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"营养值 (page does not exist)\")，甜瓜只需1回合即可吃完。\n\n[投掷](/index.php?title=%E6%8A%95%E6%8E%B7\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"投掷 (page does not exist)\")甜瓜会摧毁之（“啪嗒！”）[\\[3\\]](#cite_note-3)。\n\n## 策略\n\n甜瓜是不错的小食，不过不要试图用它来驯服、安抚或喂食[家畜](/index.php?title=%E5%AE%B6%E7%95%9C\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"家畜 (page does not exist)\")，因为它只要被投掷出去就会摔烂。\n\n甜瓜的字符颜色与[美杜莎](/index.php?title=%E7%BE%8E%E6%9D%9C%E8%8E%8E\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"美杜莎 (page does not exist)\")的[尸体](/wiki/%E5%B0%B8%E4%BD%93 \"尸体\")相同，如果不慎弄混，有可能造成[YASD](/index.php?title=YASD/zh-CN\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"YASD/zh-CN (page does not exist)\")。\n\n## 历史\n\n甜瓜最初于[Jay Fenlason's Hack](/wiki/Jay_Fenlason%27s_Hack \"Jay Fenlason's Hack\")的衍生作品Hack for PDP-11里出现，也是[Hack 1.0](/wiki/Hack_1.0 \"Hack 1.0\")中最初加入游戏的物品之一。\n\n## Variants\n\n**此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。**  \n您可以帮助我们[**翻译此页面**](https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Melon/zh-CN\\&action=edit)，但**请勿使用机器翻译**。\n\n### UnNetHack\n\nIn [UnNetHack](/wiki/UnNetHack \"UnNetHack\"), the \"Pacman\" [random vault](/wiki/Random_vault_\\(UnNetHack\\) \"Random vault (UnNetHack)\") has a melon among the randomly placed 'fruit' items.\n\nBoth maps for the top floor of the [Ruins of Moria](/wiki/Ruins_of_Moria \"Ruins of Moria\") have a melon on the outside of the main gate, placed atop an [engraving](/wiki/Engraving \"Engraving\") that can only be read at night: \"Speak, friend, and enter\". This is a pun on \"mellon\", which is elvish for \"friend\" in [J.R.R. Tolkien](/wiki/J.R.R._Tolkien \"J.R.R. Tolkien\")'s setting of Middle-Earth.\n\n### SpliceHack\n\nIn [SpliceHack](/wiki/SpliceHack \"SpliceHack\"), the defunct [Dancer](/wiki/Dancer \"Dancer\") role starts the game with a melon among their initial food items.\n\n## 百科文本\n\n\"What is it, Umbopa, son of a fool?\" I shouted in Zulu.  \n\"It is food and water, Macumazahn,\" and again he waved the  \ngreen thing.  \nThen I saw what he had got. It was a melon. We had hit upon  \na patch of wild melons, thousands of them, and dead ripe.  \n\"Melons!\" I yelled to Good, who was next me; and in another  \nsecond he had his false teeth fixed in one.  \nI think we ate about six each before we had done, and, poor  \nfruit as they were, I doubt if I ever thought anything nicer.\n\n\\[ King Solomon's Mines, by H. Rider Haggard ]\n\n## 引用及注释\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [src/u\\_init.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 144](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/u_init.c#L144)\n2. [↑](#cite_ref-2) [src/mkobj.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 2219](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/mkobj.c#L2219)\n3. [↑](#cite_ref-3) [src/dothrow.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 2067](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/dothrow.c#L2067)\n\n[![此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。](/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png)](/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version \"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\")\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Melon/zh-CN - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Melon/zh-CN\",\"wgTitle\":\"Melon/zh-CN\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":175434,\"wgRevisionId\":175434,\"wgArticleId\":40808,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"待翻译页面\",\"Encyclopedia\",\"Nethack-367 articles\",\"Comestibles/zh-CN\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Melon/zh-CN\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":40808,\"wgRequestId\":\"04652f44f72224c543ea44d5\",\"wgCSPNonce\":false,\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[],\"wgWikiEditorEnabledModules\":[],\"wgCategoryTreePageCategoryOptions\":\"{\\\"mode\\\":0,\\\"hideprefix\\\":20,\\\"showcount\\\":true,\\\"namespaces\\\":false}\"});mw.loader.state({\"site.styles\":\"ready\",\"noscript\":\"ready\",\"user.styles\":\"ready\",\"user\":\"ready\",\"user.options\":\"ready\",\"user.tokens\":\"loading\",\"ext.cite.styles\":\"ready\",\"mediawiki.legacy.shared\":\"ready\",\"mediawiki.legacy.