lass=\"new\" title=\"营养值 (page does not exist)\">100</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>食用所需回合数\n</th>\n<td>1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">5</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>行为\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"行为 (page does not exist)\">绝对素食</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>甜瓜</b>（melon）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%8F%AF%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"可食用品\">可食用品</a>。它是<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%B4%A0%E9%A3%9F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"素食 (page does not exist)\">素食</a>类食物，适合于<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E7%B4%A0%E9%A3%9F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"绝对素食 (page does not exist)\">绝对素食</a>行为。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">描述</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#UnNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">UnNetHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#SpliceHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">SpliceHack</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">百科文本</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p>甜瓜在随机生成食物中占比<sup>1</sup>&#8260;<sub>100</sub>（1%）。\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%B8%B8%E5%AE%A2&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"游客 (page does not exist)\">游客</a>在游戏开始时获得的随机食物里有可能出现甜瓜<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"使用 (page does not exist)\">使用</a>有<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%85%85%E8%83%BD&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"充能 (page does not exist)\">充能</a>的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E4%B8%B0%E9%A5%B6%E4%B9%8B%E8%A7%92&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"丰饶之角 (page does not exist)\">丰饶之角</a>有<sup>9</sup>&#8260;<sub>1000</sub>（0.9%）的概率产出1&#xff5e;2个甜瓜<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"描述\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\">描述</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"食用\">食用</a>甜瓜会获得100<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%90%A5%E5%85%BB%E5%80%BC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"营养值 (page does not exist)\">营养值</a>，甜瓜只需1回合即可吃完。\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%8A%95%E6%8E%B7&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"投掷 (page does not exist)\">投掷</a>甜瓜会摧毁之（“啪嗒！”）<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>甜瓜是不错的小食，不过不要试图用它来驯服、安抚或喂食<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%AE%B6%E7%95%9C&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"家畜 (page does not exist)\">家畜</a>，因为它只要被投掷出去就会摔烂。\n</p><p>甜瓜的字符颜色与<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%BE%8E%E6%9D%9C%E8%8E%8E&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"美杜莎 (page does not exist)\">美杜莎</a>的<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%B0%B8%E4%BD%93\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"尸体\">尸体</a>相同，如果不慎弄混，有可能造成<a href=\"/index.php?title=YASD/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"YASD/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">YASD</a>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>甜瓜最初于<a href=\"/wiki/Jay_Fenlason%27s_Hack\" title=\"Jay Fenlason&#39;s Hack\">Jay Fenlason's Hack</a>的衍生作品Hack for PDP-11里出现，也是<a href=\"/wiki/Hack_1.0\" title=\"Hack 1.0\">Hack 1.0</a>中最初加入游戏的物品之一。\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Melon/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"UnNetHack\">UnNetHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/UnNetHack\" title=\"UnNetHack\">UnNetHack</a>, the \"Pacman\" <a href=\"/wiki/Random_vault_(UnNetHack)\" title=\"Random vault (UnNetHack)\">random vault</a> has a melon among the randomly placed 'fruit' items.\n</p><p>Both maps for the top floor of the <a href=\"/wiki/Ruins_of_Moria\" title=\"Ruins of Moria\">Ruins of Moria</a> have a melon on the outside of the main gate, placed atop an <a href=\"/wiki/Engraving\" title=\"Engraving\">engraving</a> that can only be read at night: \"Speak, friend, and enter\". This is a pun on \"mellon\", which is elvish for \"friend\" in <a href=\"/wiki/J.R.R._Tolkien\" title=\"J.R.R. Tolkien\">J.R.R. Tolkien</a>'s setting of Middle-Earth.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"SpliceHack\">SpliceHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/SpliceHack\" title=\"SpliceHack\">SpliceHack</a>, the defunct <a href=\"/wiki/Dancer\" title=\"Dancer\">Dancer</a> role starts the game with a melon among their initial food items.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"百科文本\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\">百科文本</span></h2><div class=\"nhencyclopedia\">\n<div class=\"poem\">\n<p>\"What is it, Umbopa, son of a fool?\" I shouted in Zulu.<br />\n\"It is food and water, Macumazahn,\" and again he waved the<br />\ngreen thing.<br />\nThen I saw what he had got.  It was a melon.  We had hit upon<br />\na patch of wild melons, thousands of them, and dead ripe.<br />\n\"Melons!\" I yelled to Good, who was next me; and in another<br />\nsecond he had his false teeth fixed in one.<br />\nI think we ate about six each before we had done, and, poor<br />\nfruit as they were, I doubt if I ever thought anything nicer.<br />\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:right\">[ King Solomon's Mines, by H. Rider Haggard ] </div>\n</div></div>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/u_init.c#L144\">src/u_init.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 144</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/mkobj.c#L2219\">src/mkobj.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 2219</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/dothrow.c#L2067\">src/dothrow.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 2067</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926184600\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.038 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.109 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 555/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2528/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5536/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1281/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2072/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   71.560      1 -total\n 29.15%   20.861      1 Template:Languages\n 17.26%   12.349      5 Template:Languages/Lang\n 15.42%   11.037      3 Template:Refsrc\n  8.34%    5.971      3 Template:Refsrc/link\n  8.18%    5.852      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\n  7.86%    5.622      1 Template:波浪线\n  7.40%    5.293      1 Template:Translation/zh-CN\n  6.95%    4.971      1 Template:Comest