h=\"88\" height=\"31\"/></a>\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgPageParseReport\":{\"limitreport\":{\"cputime\":\"0.038\",\"walltime\":\"0.109\",\"ppvisitednodes\":{\"value\":555,\"limit\":1000000},\"ppgeneratednodes\":{\"value\":2528,\"limit\":1000000},\"postexpandincludesize\":{\"value\":5536,\"limit\":2097152},\"templateargumentsize\":{\"value\":1281,\"limit\":2097152},\"expansiondepth\":{\"value\":9,\"limit\":40},\"expensivefunctioncount\":{\"value\":4,\"limit\":100},\"unstrip-depth\":{\"value\":1,\"limit\":20},\"unstrip-size\":{\"value\":2072,\"limit\":5000000},\"timingprofile\":[\"100.00%   71.560      1 -total\",\" 29.15%   20.861      1 Template:Languages\",\" 17.26%   12.349      5 Template:Languages/Lang\",\" 15.42%   11.037      3 Template:Refsrc\",\"  8.34%    5.971      3 Template:Refsrc/link\",\"  8.18%    5.852      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\",\"  7.86%    5.622      1 Template:波浪线\",\"  7.40%    5.293      1 Template:Translation/zh-CN\",\"  6.95%    4.971      1 Template:Comestible/zh-CN\",\"  5.65%    4.044      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240926184600\",\"ttl\":604800,\"transientcontent\":false}}});mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":182});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{needhelp/zh-CN}}\n{{languages}}\n{{comestible/zh-CN\n  |color=brightgreen\n  |name=甜瓜\n  |tile=[[image:melon.png]]\n  |cost=10\n  |nutrition=100\n  |turns=1\n  |weight=5\n  |conduct=绝对素食\n}}\n'''甜瓜'''（melon）是{{cnlink|NetHack}}中的一种[[可食用品]]。它是[[素食]]类食物，适合于[[绝对素食]]行为。\n\n== 生成 ==\n甜瓜在随机生成食物中占比{{frac|100}}（1%）。\n\n[[游客]]在游戏开始时获得的随机食物里有可能出现甜瓜{{refsrc|src/u_init.c|144|version=NetHack 3.6.7}}。\n\n[[使用]]有[[充能]]的[[丰饶之角]]有{{frac|9|1000}}（0.9%）的概率产出1{{波浪线}}2个甜瓜{{refsrc|src/mkobj.c|2219|version=NetHack 3.6.7}}。\n\n== 描述 ==\n[[食用]]甜瓜会获得100[[营养值]]，甜瓜只需1回合即可吃完。\n\n[[投掷]]甜瓜会摧毁之（“啪嗒！”）{{refsrc|src/dothrow.c|2067|nethack=3.6.7}}。\n\n== 策略 ==\n甜瓜是不错的小食，不过不要试图用它来驯服、安抚或喂食[[家畜]]，因为它只要被投掷出去就会摔烂。\n\n甜瓜的字符颜色与[[美杜莎]]的[[尸体]]相同，如果不慎弄混，有可能造成{{cnlink|YASD}}。\n\n== 历史 ==\n甜瓜最初于[[Jay Fenlason's Hack]]的衍生作品Hack for PDP-11里出现，也是[[Hack 1.0]]中最初加入游戏的物品之一。\n\n==Variants==\n{{translation/zh-CN|n}}\n===UnNetHack===\nIn [[UnNetHack]], the \"Pacman\" [[Random vault (UnNetHack)|random vault]] has a melon among the randomly placed 'fruit' items.\n\nBoth maps for the top floor of the [[Ruins of Moria]] have a melon on the outside of the main gate, placed atop an [[engraving]] that can only be read at night: \"Speak, friend, and enter\". This is a pun on \"mellon\", which is elvish for \"friend\" in [[J.R.R. Tolkien]]'s setting of Middle-Earth.\n\n===SpliceHack===\nIn [[SpliceHack]], the defunct [[Dancer]] role starts the game with a melon among their initial food items.\n\n== 百科文本 ==\n{{encyclopedia|\n\"What is it, Umbopa, son of a fool?\" I shouted in Zulu.\n\"It is food and water, Macumazahn,\" and again he waved the\ngreen thing.\nThen I saw what he had got.  It was a melon.  We had hit upon\na patch of wild melons, thousands of them, and dead ripe.\n\"Melons!\" I yelled to Good, who was next me; and in another\nsecond he had his false teeth fixed in one.\nI think we ate about six each before we had done, and, poor\nfruit as they were, I doubt if I ever thought anything nicer.\n|[ King Solomon's Mines, by H. Rider Haggard ]\n}}\n\n== 引用及注释 ==\n<references/>\n{{nethack-367/zh-CN}}\n[[Category:Comestibles/zh-CN|TIANGUA]]"}